[34m│[0m ## XSS (Cross-Site Scripting) Attack Playbook                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > **IMPORTANT:** All payloads in this playbook are EXAMPLES that must be     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m MODIFIED for your specific target. Replace placeholders like                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m `{ATTACKER_URL}`, `{PAYLOAD}`, `{TARGET_URL}` with actual values. Adapt      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m payloads based on:                                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - Target application's filtering/WAF behavior                              [34m│[0m
