[34m│[0m ### XSS Types                                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - **Reflected XSS**: Malicious code in link, executed when victim clicks     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - **Stored XSS**: Malicious code stored on server, executes on page access   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - **DOM-based XSS**: Code executed in browser, not sent to server            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Proof of Concept Best Practices                                          [34m│[0m
